description: Embrace urban living in this stylish condo nestled in the heart of South Boston's vibrant west side. Flooded with natural light, thanks to the bright East and South facing windows, this flat offers an inviting atmosphere that feels like home when you step inside. Savor the convenience of a modern, open-concept kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinetry - perfect for culinary enthusiasts. The spacious living room becomes a cozy retreat with its warm gas fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for relaxation or entertaining. This condo boasts coveted amenities including garage parking, central air conditioning, hardwood floors, the practicality of an in-unit washer/dryer, and additional private storage in the basement. HVAC system in 2016 and a new garage roof in 2019, peace of mind is part of the package. Steps away from some of Southie's most popular dining spots, this is a gem that offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience.
